articleContent: Get to know this week’s Pet of the Week, a real superstar from our Bonita shelter, Estrella! Estrella is a playful and energetic Australian cattle dog mix who is looking for a new forever home where she would prefer to be an only pet. If you’re interested in adopting Estrella, please visit www.SDDAC.com.
